[DIGITAL EFFECT]

00:00:00.900 --> 00:00:03.840 align:middle line:10%
>> Searching for intelligent
life in the universe?

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:06.090 align:middle line:10%
Then look for their
energy source.

00:00:06.090 --> 00:00:10.040 align:middle line:10%
An update on the hunt
for Dyson spheres.

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:11.864 align:middle line:90%
This is Gaia News.

00:00:11.864 --> 00:00:13.792 align:middle line:90%
